name: kevin white
text: Pizza is way to greasy got a whole pie took a bite out of a slice way to greasy grease was draining  pizza is not very good if you ask my opinion I will not be eating there again

text: 2 for 2 on getting sick after eating here. Can't believe I gave them a second try.

text: They are very friendly, have good deals, and have amazing food!
